'''Davrilat''' was a complicated religion based on the sanctity of [[Music/Legends|harmonics]]. The [[Tocoyan]] [[Neb Dulo]], a [[Homeworld/Legends|native]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tocoya]], became one of Davrilat's disciples by the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].<ref name="CCG">{{CCG|set=Special Edition Limited|cardname=Neb Dulo}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
[[Decipher]] created Davrilat in [[1998]] for Neb Dulo's card in the ''[[Special Edition Limited]]'' expansion set of the [[Star Wars Customizable Card Game|''Star Wars'' Customizable Card Game]].<ref name="CCG" />

